%description
Koji-tool is a CLI interface to Koji with commands to query builds, tasks,
install rpms, and track buildlog sizes.

Koji is the RPM-based buildsystem of Fedora Linux and CentOS.


%prep
# Begin cabal-rpm setup:
%setup -q
